songs.title: Yawa
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Ice
Ice Prince Zamani
Peruzzi
Efya come make you listen
Old age e bi you wey dey bang for my system
Kojo call your sister
I get plan
Damnn…Ice
Peruzzi

[Chorus – Peruzzi]
I’ll give you my life
Hold ground for you, make you my wife
I no need to lie
If Yawa no go dey
And if I get chance for you
I’ll come through for you
You go know my plan for you
If Yawa no go dey
